@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam defaultFontName WenQuanYi Micro Hei
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam maxmessagesize 140
skinparam ParticipantPadding 30
skinparam BoxPadding 8

title 企业RAG — 运维操作流程

actor 运维人员 as Ops
participant "launch.sh\n(应用管理)" as Launch
participant "infra.sh\n(基础服务管理)" as Infra
participant "Docker CLI\n(docker-compose)" as Docker
collections "基础设施\nMySQL / Redis / ES\nKafka / MinIO" as InfraSvc

== 1. 日常巡检 ==

Ops -> Infra: ./infra.sh status
Infra -> InfraSvc: curl ES _cluster/health
InfraSvc --> Infra: green / yellow / red
Infra -> InfraSvc: kafka-topics --list (topic + 积压)
InfraSvc --> Infra: file-processing / vectorization
Infra --> Ops: 各服务健康状态汇总

Ops -> Docker: docker ps --format "table {{.Names}}\\n{{.Status}}"
Docker --> Ops: 5 个容器运行状态

Ops -> Launch: ./launch.sh status
Launch --> Ops: 应用 PID + CPU/MEM + 最近日志

== 2. 应用部署与回滚 ==

Ops -> Launch: ./launch.sh start
Launch -> Launch: git pull → mvn package -DskipTests
Launch -> InfraSvc: kill 旧进程 (读取 pid.log)
Launch -> Launch: 加载 .env 环境变量\njava -jar -Xms1g -Xmx1g
Launch -> InfraSvc: 新进程监听 :8081
Launch --> Ops: 编译 → 部署 → 启动完成

Ops -> Launch: ./launch.sh restart (快速重启)
Launch -> InfraSvc: kill 旧进程
Launch -> Launch: 直接启动已有 jar
Launch --> Ops: 重启完成，新 PID 已记录

Ops -> Launch: ./launch.sh stop (回滚)
Launch -> InfraSvc: kill 进程
Launch --> Ops: 应用已停止

== 3. 应急处置 ==

Ops -> Docker: docker-compose restart <service>
Docker -> InfraSvc: 停止容器 → 启动新容器
Docker --> Ops: 容器重启完成

Ops -> InfraSvc: curl -XPOST ES _forcemerge\n?only_expunge_deletes=true
InfraSvc --> Ops: 索引碎片清理完成

Ops -> InfraSvc: kafka-consumer-groups --reset-offsets\n--group file-processing-group --to-earliest
InfraSvc --> Ops: 消费组重置，积压重新消费

Ops -> InfraSvc: redis-cli INFO memory
InfraSvc --> Ops: used_memory / maxmemory\n(超 80% 需清理或扩容)

@enduml
